### ==== ORGANIZATION API ====
# Docs: http://localhost:5000/scalar/v1
# Base routes:
#   /api/v1/admin/org/units    — org unit CRUD + tree + members (Admin for writes)
#   /api/v1/admin/org/staff    — staff assignment + transfer + history (Admin only)
#
# All endpoints require tenantId as query param.
# Org unit tree: flat list — clients build hierarchy from parentId field.

# ── Org Units ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get full org unit tree (flat list, build hierarchy from parentId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/units?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get single org unit by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/units/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get active members of an org unit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/units/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/members?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create org unit (Admin/SystemAdmin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/units?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Phòng Quản lý Đất đai",
  "nameEn": "Land Management Department",
  "code": "LMD-001",
  "parentId": null
}

###

### Create child org unit under a parent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/units?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bộ phận Cấp phép",
  "nameEn": "Licensing Division",
  "code": "LMD-001-LIC",
  "parentId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

###

### Update org unit name fields (Admin/SystemAdmin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/units/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Phòng Quản lý Đất đai và Tài nguyên",
  "nameEn": "Land and Resource Management Department"
}

###

### Soft-delete org unit (Admin/SystemAdmin — blocked if active children exist)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/units/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Soft-delete with successor unit (reassigns members)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/units/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?tenantId={{tenantId}}&successorId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── Staff Assignments ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Assign user to an org unit with role and position title (Admin/SystemAdmin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/staff/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002/assign?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orgUnitId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "roleInOrg": "Officer",
  "positionTitle": "Chuyên viên Quản lý Đất đai"
}

###

### Transfer user to a new org unit (closes old assignment, opens new one)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/staff/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002/transfer?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toOrgUnitId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
  "roleInOrg": "SeniorOfficer",
  "positionTitle": "Chuyên viên Chính"
}

###

### Get full assignment and position history for a user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/org/staff/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002/history?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
